graph LR
    CFOp["CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.16.0"]

    %% External Dependencies (libraries/frameworks)
    CFOp -->|"controller framework<br/>v0.19.3"| CtrlRuntime["controller-runtime"]
    CFOp -->|"RayCluster CRD types<br/>v1.2.1"| KubeRayAPI["kuberay ray-operator API"]
